name: Cabbage Clicker Game
description:
CABBAGE CLICKER

Cabbage Clicker is a free to play clicker/idle game, where your goal is to gain enough cabbages to ascend, and become the holy cabbage! You can speed up your journey to Cabbage Ascension by spending your cabbages on upgrades. Upgrades include increased cabbages per second, click power, and unlocking special features!

NOTE:  All my games I release for free, but there is always the option to donate! It would help out more then you think, but if you want to download the game for free, after clicking download, just click: "No thanks, just take me to the download"
